Interface Summary
CloneAttributeMeta HL7 v3 Specification(H3S) Attribute Meta Class

CloneChoiceMeta A choice kind of clone meta class
CloneDatatypeFieldMeta Description of the class
CloneMeta HL7 Clone Class meta information used for mapping purpose.
CloneMultipleMeta A multiple kind of clone meta class whose cardinality is 0..* or 1..*
HL7V3Meta The HL7 V3 Meta is the specialization of the HL7 v3 meta information that reflects an end-user’s customization of the HL7 v3 meta information.
